commendationservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "redis-cart-0", "shippingservice-0", "shippingservice-1", "shippingservice-2"], "metric_name": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "pod_cpu_usage", "request", "response", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"]}, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["frontend-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "emailservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "currencyservice-0", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-1", "checkoutservice-2", "cartservice-1", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["cartservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "emailservice-0", "adservice-1", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "adservice-2", "checkoutservice-1", "currencyservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "frontend-2"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault occurred from 2025-06-19T06:10:19Z to 2025-06-19T06:28:19Z. Please identify the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-19 06:10:19+00:00 to 2025-06-19 06:28:19+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["frontend-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "emailservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "currencyservice-0", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-1", "checkoutservice-2", "cartservice-1", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["cartservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "emailservice-0", "adservice-1", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "adservice-2", "checkoutservice-1", "currencyservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "frontend-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "pod_cpu_usage", "request", "response", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"], "trace_analysis_findings": "以下是对调用链数据的初步分析结果：\n\n### 探测到的延迟和错误\n\n1. **延迟倍数分析 (rrt_max):**\n   - `checkoutservice->cartservice`: 延迟倍数非常高，`POST /hipstershop.CartService/GetCart` 从正常约 2495 ms 增加到超过 18146 ms。\n   - `cartservice->redis`: Redis 的 HGET 操作延迟显著增加，从正常约 1739 ms 增加到 22624 ms。\n\n2. **错误状态 (error_ratio):**\n   - `frontend->CurrencyService`: 高频率的连接错误 `connection refused`。\n   - 在 `checkoutservice->CurrencyService` 的过程中也观察到了频繁的连接错误。\n\n### 错误起始点和延迟根因\n- **根因定位**:\n  - 调用链从 `frontend` 开始失败，但 `CurrencyService` 显示了多个连接被拒绝的错误。\n  - `checkoutservice` 调用 `cartservice` 期间显示高延迟和 Redis 访问异常。\n\n### 关键假设\n- **CurrencyService** 可能存在问题，导致连接被拒绝 (`error_ratio`)。\n- **CheckoutService 和 CartService** 之间的交互可能因 Redis 访问时间过长而导致高延迟 (`rrt_max`)。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"checkoutservice->cartservice\", \"cartservice->redis\", \"error_ratio\", \"frontend->CurrencyService\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CurrencyService\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: connection refused\\\"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"POST /hipstershop.CartService/GetCart duration increased from 2495ms to 18146ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"HGET operation duration increased from 1739ms to 22624ms\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n需要进一步深入分析，以确认这些初步假设。特别是关注 `CurrencyService` 的可用性和 `CartService` 对 Redis 的依赖关系。", "log_analysis_findings": "### 分析发现\n\n从日志中发现以下异常模式和相关服务信息：\n\n1. **Connection Error**\n   - **关键词**: `transport`, `Error while dialing`, `connection refused`\n   - **涉及组件**: \"frontend\"\n   - **根本原因**: 日志中多次出现类似 `transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.39.78:7000: connect: connection refused`，表明 frontend 服务无法与某个目标服务进行连接，通常是端口配置信息不正确。\n   - **关键日志片段**: \n     ```plaintext\n     \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.39.78:7000: connect: connection refused\"\n     ```\n\n2. **Internal Error**\n   - **关键词**: `rpc error`, `failed to complete the order`, `failed to convert price`\n   - **涉及组件**: \"frontend\"\n   - **根本原因**: 日志中出现 `failed to prepare order: failed to convert price`，可能与系统内的货币转换服务应用程序的问题有关。\n   - **关键日志片段**:\n     ```plaintext\n     \"rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to prepare order: failed to convert price\"\n     ```\n\n3. **Service Availability**\n   - **关键词**: `Transport is closing`\n   - **涉及组件**: \"frontend\"\n   - **根本原因**: 出现 `transport is closing` 表明服务可能因过载或资源不足而无法继续处理请求，导致连接被关闭。\n   - **关键日志片段**:\n     ```plaintext\n     \"rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = transport is closing\"\n     ```\n\n### 输出\n\n根据以上发现，生成的输出如下：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"transport\", \"Error while dialing\", \"connection refused\", \"rpc error\", \"failed to convert price\", \"Transport is closing\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Connection refused possibly due to port misconfiguration.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.39.78:7000: connect: connection refused\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Failed price conversions may be linked to internal application errors.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to prepare order: failed to convert price\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Transport closure indicates possible resource or load-related issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = transport is closing\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n此报告有助于进一步的故障排查和定位具体问题，可以考虑从网络配置和资源监控等方面着手分析。", "metric_analysis_findings": "初始扫描数据显示以下异常调用链和指标：\n\n### 异常指标关键点\n- **错误率异常**：多个服务的 `error_ratio` 和 `client_error_ratio` 显著增加，尤其是 `frontend`, `shippingservice`, `adservice`。这些指标显示了高达 43.75 的 P99 变化。\n- **响应时间异常**：服务的 `rrt_max` 显著变化，包括 `frontend`, `checkoutservice`, `currencyservice` 等。\n- **Pod CPU 使用率**：`currencyservice-2`, `frontend-0`, `frontend-1`, `productcatalogservice-1` 等显示 CPU 使用率变化。\n\n### 异常实体分析\n1. **Frontend 服务**：\n   - 异常指标：`error_ratio`, `server_error_ratio`, `rrt_max`\n   - 影响 Pod：`frontend-0`, `frontend-1`, `frontend-2`\n   - 原因：潜在的错误处理不足或服务过载。\n   \n2. **Shippingservice 服务**：\n   - 异常指标：`client_error_ratio`, `error_ratio`\n   - 影响 Pod：`shippingservice-0`, `shippingservice-1`, `shippingservice-2`\n   - 原因：客户端请求错误增多，可能的接口问题或服务不可用。\n   \n3. **Currencyservice 服务**\n   - 异常指标：`rrt_max`, `pod_cpu_usage`\n   - 异常 Pod：`currencyservice-2`\n   - 原因：高响应时间可能由于 CPU 资源不足或计算任务负载过高。\n\n4. **Adservice 服务**：\n   - 异常指标：`error_ratio`, `client_error_ratio`\n   - 异常 Pod：`adservice-2`\n   - 原因：请求和响应错误显著增加，可能服务接口问题。\n\n### JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"server_error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"高 error_ratio 和 rrt_max，服务性能受限，导致请求处理延迟。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio 在故障时 P99 从 0.0 至 43.75，rrt_max 从 288863.0 至 34833.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"client_error_ratio 和 error_ratio 激增，表明请求处理错误。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio P99 从 0.0 至 31.66\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"异常 CPU 使用率和 rrt_max，指示可能的资源瓶颈。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage 从 0.04 至 0.0，rrt_max 从 14360.0 至 4256.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"高错误率，指示请求处理异常。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio 在故障时 P99 变更显著\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n请仔细审核这些异常实体和指标以深入确认根因。前端和货运服务的请求错误比例显著和响应时间峰值指出了可能的资源配置问题或服务配置错误。后续分析应聚焦于这些服务的具体实现方式、负载测试结果以及流量模式。"}
